data.description: Have you been looking for a country house in a small town with land and views? Wait no longer! This is the home you have been waiting for! Sits on 4.68 acres (MOL) and features 3 beds and 3 full baths. This 2265 sq ft house offers so much STORAGE and open space. The land has so many trees, offering shade for all your outside events with family and friends! Recent updates include roof, water softener, flooring, bathroom and more! Wait no longer, and SCHEDULE A SHOWING TODAY!
